---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Behind the Curtain: The Private Lives of Hollywood Stars" description="Peek into the enigmatic world of celebrity private lives at StarGossip Hub. From whispered romances and family bliss to hidden hobbies, we uncover the glamorous secrets that make stars human, all with our signature Hollywood elegance.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#610023] via-[#8a0033] to-[#610023] py-24">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block bg-[#ff6f61] text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider">
          <i class="fas fa-crown mr-2"></i> EXCLUSIVE CONTENT
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Behind the Curtain
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-[#ff6f61] mb-8">
          The Private Lives of Hollywood Stars
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Peek into the enigmatic world of celebrity private lives at StarGossip Hub. From whispered romances and family bliss to hidden hobbies, we uncover the glamorous secrets that make stars human, all with our signature Hollywood elegance.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#ff6f61] rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Romantic Escapades Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#f8f4f5]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#610023] mb-4">Romantic Escapades and Secret Affairs</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#ff6f61] mx-auto"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Love in Hollywood is a blockbuster waiting to happen—or unravel. Discover the <span class="font-bold italic text-[#610023]">steamy</span> romances that bloom in private jets and secluded beaches.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#610023] to-[#8a0033] relative">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Timothée Chalamet & Kylie Jenner</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-heart text-[#ff6f61] text-xl mr-2"></i>
              <span class="font-bold text-[#610023]">Whispers of a Passionate Fling</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Whispers of a passionate fling that started at a hidden Malibu retreat. Their relationship remains one of the most intriguing celebrity romances of recent years, blending cinematic charm with real-world romance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8a0033] to-[#610023] relative">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Brad Pitt's Reclusive Retreats</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-mountain text-[#ff6f61] text-xl mr-2"></i>
              <span class="font-bold text-[#610023]">The Actor's Quiet Escapes</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              The actor's quiet escapes to remote locations away from the glare of fame. These secluded moments provide the perfect contrast to his Hollywood persona, revealing a more introspective side of the entertainment icon.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Family & Hobbies Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f8f4f5] to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#610023] mb-4">Family Bliss & Hidden Hobbies</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#ff6f61] mx-auto"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Beyond the glittering stage, Hollywood stars discover the beauty of simplicity in family moments and unexpected passions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#610023] to-[#8a0033] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white h-full transform transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.03]">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Family Moments</h3>
            <p class="opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
              Celebrity families hide beautiful traditions and moments of domestic bliss. From children's birthday parties to family vacations, the real magic happens in these intimate settings away from the spotlight.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#ff6f61] to-[#ff9a91] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white h-full transform transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.03]">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Hidden Hobbies</h3>
            <p class="opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
              Many stars indulge in artistic pursuits and creative hobbies that surprise fans. Whether it's painting, gardening, or photography, these passions reveal a more human side of Tinseltown's elite.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#610023] to-[#4d001a] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white h-full transform transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.03]">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Culinary Adventures</h3>
            <p class="opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
              Behind closed doors, Hollywood chefs and culinary enthusiasts showcase their passion for food. From secret cooking classes to exclusive restaurant discoveries, culinary adventures are just as glamorous as the films they star in.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TV Show Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#610023] to-[#8a0033] text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">The Inside Scoop</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#ff6f61] mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="font-bold">StarGossip Hub</span> brings you exclusive insights into Hollywood's most secretive corners, where the magic of celebrity life meets the reality of human experience.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white border-opacity-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#ff6f61] flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="fas fa-star text-white text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg italic mb-6">
            "We're not just reporting on Hollywood—we're revealing the stories that make the stars truly unforgettable."
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#ff6f61] font-bold">— The StarGossip Hub Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff6f61] to-[#ff9a91]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">Unlock Hollywood's Private World</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join thousands of fans who subscribe to our exclusive celebrity insights and never miss a moment of Hollywood's private life.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <button class="bg-[#610023] hover:bg-[#4d001a] text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
            Subscribe Now
          </button>
          <button class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-[#610023] font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
            <i class="fas fa-star mr-2"></i> Latest Updates
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>